Run test pmd on dpdk-22 version: go to /build/app
run the command:
./dpdk-testpmd  -n 4 -- -i --port-topology=chained

then type :set fwd txonly
then type start



to capture it : open one more secondary instance of dpdk on 22 version and then go to build/app and type:

./build/app/dpdk-dumpcap  -i 1 -c 6 -w /tmp/capture.pcap


THe pcap file will get saved

